Package: Evoluty
Type: Package
Title: Evolutionary Computation Techniques
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Carlos Vázquez Losada
Maintainer: Carlos Vázquez Losada <c.vazquezlosada@gmail.com>
Description: Evoluty contains techniques, approaches and algorithms of Evolutionary
      Computation. At the moment, it contains Grammar-Guided Genetic Programming
      implementations for both general purposes and a peculiar implementation
      of a general purpose algorithm that fixes a unresolved problem: Get the
      best neural network for a given problem by using Grammar-Guided Genetic 
      Programming.
